None.Name: Infused Morphing
None.Description:
Activate to
transform an own ground unit within
a 100m range into a Mutating Frenzy
that has its special Deathwish
already activated. Thus it deals 75%
more damage but also loses 90 life
points every 2 seconds. Mutating
Frenzy has the same upgrade level as
the building itself. Reusable every 20
seconds.
